OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is still deducting money
OL,6, from people's Universal Credit to pay  
OL,7, their utility bills, despite it losing 
OL,8, a legal case concerning other benefits.
OL,10,FLast year, High Court judges said a    
OL,11,Fscheme - which allows money to be taken
OL,12,Ffrom people claiming benefits to pay   
OL,13,Fenergy bills - was unlawful if the     
OL,14,Fclaimant had not first consented.      
OL,16,FBut the ruling did not cover people on 
OL,17,FUniversal Credit and BBC News has found
OL,18,Fthousands are still having money taken.
OL,20,FThe government says the policy is fair.
